description: The fund is a "fund of funds" that employs a "passive management"-or indexing-investment approach designed to track the performance of the index. The index consists of an investible portfolio of ETFs ("Underlying ETFs") with exposure to major U.S. and non-U.S. asset classes. The advisor attempts to invest all, or substantially all, of its assets in the securities that make up the index.
name: Premise Capital Diversified Tactical ETF
